Same in EW...  the Dain outpost between the pit and the bridge is prolly never gonna be trained (they won't kill the animals)...   the Dain outpost between the pit and the GD zone is more likely to be trained by an overpull of giants or orcs out of the pit or from the giant fort...<br>
