<br>
I understand the Dain are there for faction, but you do not think they were put at that precise location for a reason?  The mob pathing does not collide so they fight on thier own.  You think that VI put up a map on the wall and threw darts for mob locations?  I do not expect them to be there so &quot;save&quot; me or anyone else for that matter, but they were NOT just plunked right there without reason.<br>
<br>
