<br>
Yes, my original poll states that &quot;you&quot; are an asshole if you kill guards because you can or for faction or whatever...   but it is a statement, as you can see, it was selected even though it is derogetory...  I did not mean anything personally when I put it in there, but I am guessing you took it personally by your response... In my experience, when someone takes a public comment personally, it is usually because the comment has a &quot;ring&quot; of truth to it...  sorry...  ;p<br>
